data.description: Nestled near the picturesque shores of Mobile Bay, this charming 4 bedroom cottage offers a perfect blend of coastal living and modern comfort.  With 2.5 bathrooms and recent updates, this home is ready to become your ultimate beachside sanctuary.  The heart of the home boasts stainless steel appliances, elegant quartz countertops and a stylish tile backsplash creating a chef's paradise for culinary delights.  Immerse yourself in breathtaking views of Mobile Bay and the Gulf of Mexico, offering a constant reminder of the beauty of coastal living. Prepare your fresh catch with the ease at the convenient outdoor fish cleaning station/sink, perfect for anglers and seafood enthusiasts.  Rinse off the salt and sand under the open sky with the convenient outdoor shower providing a refreshing experience after a day at the beach.  Don't miss your opportunity to own a slice of paradise on the Alabama Gulf Coast.  Schedule a showing today and make this coastal cottage your own.
